rows.name:
Tons of refugees from Acedia have
arrived here in Trigo!

rows.label: tlk41400021_06_msg0002
rows.name:
This is the chance of a lifetime!
I'm going to teach them all about the
wonders of Gulan woodcrafts!

rows.label: tlk41400021_06_msg0003
rows.name:
One look at my beautiful woodcrafts,
and I'm sure they'll forget all about
their woes!
